OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FUnregulated resale markets abroad
OL,7,Fcould be driving a spike in brazen
OL,8,Fattacks, as ITV News' Kaf Okpattah
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FA growing threat of "smash-and-grab"
OL,12,Fraids on jewellers has been fuelled by
OL,13,Frising precious metal prices and
OL,14,Foverseas resale demand, according to
OL,15,Fexclusive data from an industry group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
