OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FTen incidents of armed robbery in the
OL,7,FUK were reported to monitoring
OL,8,Finitiative Safer Gems within the first
OL,9,Fthree months of this year, which is up
OL,10,Ffrom just one reported incident last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThis resulted in a total loss of #3.2
OL,14,Fmillion worth of goods, and marks a
OL,15,Fsignificant increase from the same
OL,16,Fperiod in 2025, where #60,000 of
OL,17,Flosses were reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
