FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FSmash and grabs involve criminals
OL,7,Fusing weapons or cars to ram their way
OL,8,Finto jewellers and luxury stores
OL,9,Fbefore making off with goods.
OL,11,FFor jewellers and pawnbrokers, the
OL,12,Floss of goods can be a blow, but the
OL,13,Fimpact of the crime goes beyond the
OL,14,Fvalue of the items themselves.
OL,16,FIn January 2025, Dave Mandry-Jones was
OL,17,Fworking at Brooklands Jewellers when a
OL,18,Fstolen car repeatedly rammed into the
OL,19,Fshop front.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,F"It was quite frightening at the time,
OL,7,Fbecause you don't know how far they're
OL,8,Fgoing to come into the shop. Are they
OL,9,Farmed, are they not?" he told us.
OL,11,F"So we took safety in the back of the
OL,12,Fshop and waited for it all to be over."
OL,14,FPolice caught two of those responsible
OL,15,Fshortly after the incident and were
OL,16,Fable to recover the #50,000 worth of
OL,17,Fgoods stolen. The pair have since been
OL,18,Fsentenced to prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FBut Mandry-Jones and his business
OL,7,Fpartner were still hit with costs for
OL,8,Ffresh security measures, spending
OL,9,F#15,000 alone on reinforcing the shop
OL,10,Ffront. He told us that smash and grabs
OL,11,Fhave a devastating impact on victims
OL,12,Fof the crime.
OL,14,F"They just ruin people's lives. We had
OL,15,Fa whole year of trauma and stress
OL,16,Fdealing with it, for it to take 40
OL,17,Fseconds for them to get what they
OL,18,Fwanted," Dave added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
