CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FSmash and grabs have been reported up
OL,7,Fand down the country, with most taking
OL,8,Fplace in London. In the first two
OL,9,Fmonths of 2026, three London jewellers
OL,10,Fwere struck in the space of a few
OL,11,Fweeks.
OL,13,FIn February, seven men were sentenced
OL,14,Ffor a string of seven smash-and-grab
OL,15,Frobberies that took place in the city
OL,16,Fin 2025.
OL,18,F"We are seeing an increase in the
OL,19,Ftheft of jewellery such as precious
OL,20,Fmetals and diamonds," Safer Gems told
OL,21,FITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,F"Due to the high prices, gold and
OL,7,Fsilver have become attractive
OL,8,Fcommodities, which are easier to melt
OL,9,Fdown, to hide its identification and
OL,10,Fsell on."
OL,12,FBefore the impact of Iran war set in,
OL,13,Fthe price of gold in the UK reached a
OL,14,Ffive-year high of more than #4,000 per
OL,15,Founce on Monday 2 March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
