PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FHigh demand has been reported in
OL,7,FRussia, the Middle East and China for
OL,8,Fprestige watches - something stolen
OL,9,Fgoods investigator Christopher
OL,10,FMarinello from Art Recovery
OL,11,FInternational said he has come across
OL,12,Fin his work.
OL,14,FMarinello said he has seen stolen
OL,15,Fgoods end up on different continents
OL,16,Fin a matter of hours, with the UAE
OL,17,Foften appearing in his inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,F"The problem is, there's a lot of
OL,7,Fmoney in Dubai and people buy things
OL,8,Fquickly without asking any questions.
OL,9,FThere's not a lot of due diligence
OL,10,Fbeing done," he said.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FFor stolen watches remaining in the
OL,18,FUK, Safer Gems has warned that
OL,19,Fprestige models are being worn as
OL,20,Fstatus symbols following theft by gang
OL,21,Fmembers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FWhen "stolen to order", gangs will
OL,7,F"raffle out" watches to gang members
OL,8,Fto wear, the initiative told ITV News.
OL,10,FWhen it comes to preventing smash-and-
OL,11,Fgrab criminals from making off with
OL,12,Fgoods in the first place, Safer Gems
OL,13,Fis urging jewellers to install fog
OL,14,Fmachines.
OL,16,FThe technology allows shops to be
OL,17,Ffilled in seconds with an opaque fog
OL,18,Fwhich leaves no residue, in an attempt
OL,19,Fto push out thieves attempting to
OL,20,Fsteal goods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FNeil Chrismas, a representative from
OL,7,Fsecurity firm Fog Bandit, said the
OL,8,Fdemand for the technology has been
OL,9,Fgrowing.
OL,11,F"We have rising prices for gold and
OL,12,Fsilver, so among pawnbrokers and the
OL,13,Fjewellery sector particularly, there
OL,14,Fis a lot of anxiety around the levels
OL,15,Fof assets in jewellery shops and
OL,16,Fwarehouses as smash and grabs are
OL,17,Fbecoming more prevalent," he said.
OL,19,FThe use of security fog is also being
OL,20,Frecommended by police, as they
OL,21,Fcontinue to grapple with the crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing of a criminal
OL,7,Fgang in February, Detective Chief
OL,8,FInspector Scott Mather, from the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police's Flying Squad,
OL,10,Fsaid: "We realise these attacks on
OL,11,Fluxury stores have had a significant
OL,12,Fimpact on business owners and the
OL,13,Fcommunities around them.
OL,15,F"Our detectives worked quickly,
OL,16,Festablishing common patterns between
OL,17,Fthe attacks to link them to one
OL,18,Fcriminal network. Forensic analysis
OL,19,Fand fast-paced CCTV enquiries were
OL,20,Fthen able to identify the suspects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776250558
OL,3,CHow smash-and-grab raids 'ruin lives'
OL,4,C- and why the crime has been growing
OL,6,F"This is a clear message to anyone who
OL,7,Fthinks they can carry out smash-and-
OL,8,Fgrab raids in London - we will
OL,9,Fidentify you, we will track you down
OL,10,Fand we will bring you to justice."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
